<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-46-0060 </DOCNO><TEXT>Solar cars have reached the state of technical maturity. Applicationsof solar cars in urban traffic are presented (with illustrations). Solarcar races are gone into. A history and technical outline of solar carsis followed by a description of solar cars for everyday use (types, trends,designs). Acceptance testing and legal problems are gone into, and exceptsare presented of an interview with the director of an engineering school.Trends in solar car technology are mentioned in the last chapter. (HWJ).</TEXT></DOC>